le="♬ Eusexua - FKA 树枝" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/Eusexua-7413134928274425872?refer=embed">♬ Eusexua – FKA 树枝</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@twigs.archive/video/7415778048831737130" data-video-id="7415778048831737130" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@twigs.archive" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@twigs.archive?refer=embed">@twigs.archive</a></p><p> Eusexua 是我最喜欢的专辑，但它还没有发行<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />这个片段听起来很棒<a title="卡特维格斯" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/fkatwigs?refer=embed">#fkatwigs</a> <a title="树枝" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/twigs?refer=embed">#twigs</a> <a title="尤塞克阿" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/eusexua?refer=embed">#EUSEXUA</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ Eusexua - FKA 树枝" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/Eusexua-7408993910842787857?refer=embed">♬ Eusexua – FKA 树枝</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@crackmagazine/video/7415250123971726624" data-video-id="7415250123971726624" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@破解杂志" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@crackmagazine?refer=embed">@破解杂志</a></p><p>FKA Twigs 在 ON running 直播中首次推出新歌<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f6f8.png" alt="🛸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a title="卡特维格斯" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/fkatwigs?refer=embed">#fkatwigs</a> <a title="尤塞克阿" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/eusexua?refer=embed">#eusexua</a> <a title="新音乐" target="_blank" href="https://www.t